=head1 DESCRIPTION

Evidence that's manually added to a control in Audit Manager.
C<manualEvidence> can be one of the following: C<evidenceFileName>,
C<s3ResourcePath>, or C<textResponse>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 EvidenceFileName => Str

The name of the file that's uploaded as manual evidence. This name is
populated using the C<evidenceFileName> value from the
C<GetEvidenceFileUploadUrl>
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/audit-manager/latest/APIReference/API_GetEvidenceFileUploadUrl.html)
API response.


=head2 S3ResourcePath => Str

The S3 URL of the object that's imported as manual evidence.


=head2 TextResponse => Str

The plain text response that's entered and saved as manual evidence.



